[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "Every measure pursued by the commons, and, still more, every attempt made by their partisans, were full of the most inveterate hatred against the hierarchy, and showed a determined resolution of subverting the whole ecclesiastical establishment.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000005_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000005_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "This principle, which prevails so much among zealots, never displayed itself so openly as during the transactions of this whole period.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "But, notwithstanding these efforts of the commons, they could not expect the concurrence of the upper house either to this law, or to any other which they should introduce for the further limitation of royal authority.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "The majority of the peers adhered to the king, and plainly foresaw the depression of nobility, as a necessary consequence of popular usurpations on the crown.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000007_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000007_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "But the tide of popularity seized many, and carried them wide of the most established maxims of civil policy.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000007_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000007_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "These men, finding that their credit ran high with the nation, ventured to encourage those popular disorders, which, they vainly imagined, they possessed authority sufficient to regulate and control.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "In order to obtain a majority in the upper house, the commons had recourse to the populace, who on other occasions had done them such important service.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "They ordered halberts to be brought into the hall where they assembled, and thus armed themselves against those conspiracies with which, they pretended, they were hourly threatened.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000011_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000011_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "As stories of plots, however ridiculous, were willingly attended to, and were dispersed among the multitude, to whose capacity they were well adapted.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000011_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000011_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "Beale, a tailor, informed the commons that, walking in the fields, he had hearkened to the discourse of certain persons unknown to him, and had heard them talk of a most dangerous conspiracy.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000011_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000011_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "A hundred and eight ruffians, as he learned, had been appointed to murder a hundred and eight lords and commoners, and were promised rewards for these assassinations, ten pounds for each lord, forty shillings for each commoner.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "Multitudes flocked towards Westminster, and insulted the prelates and such of the lords as adhered to the crown.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000017_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000017_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "By way of reproach, these gentlemen gave the rabble the appellation of Roundheads, on account of the short cropped hair which they wore: these called the others Cavaliers.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "Meanwhile the tumults still continued, and even increased about Westminster and Whitehall.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000018_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000018_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "For this reason they protested against all laws, votes, and resolutions, as null and invalid, which should pass during the time of their constrained absence.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000018_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000018_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "This protestation, which, though just and legal, was certainly ill timed, was signed by twelve bishops, and communicated to the king, who hastily approved of it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000018_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000018_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "As soon as it was presented to the lords, that house desired a conference with the commons, whom they informed of this unexpected protestation.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000018_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000018_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "The opportunity was seized with joy and triumph.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000018_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000018_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "No man in either house ventured to speak a word in their vindication; so much displeased was every one at the egregious imprudence of which they had been guilty.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "When the commons employed in their remonstrance language so severe and indecent, they had not been actuated entirely by insolence and passion; their views were more solid and profound.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000026_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000026_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "When he considered all these increasing acts of insolence in the commons, he was apt to ascribe them in a great measure to his own indolence and facility.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000026_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000026_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "The queen and the ladies of the court further stimulated his passion, and represented that, if he exerted the vigor and displayed the majesty of a monarch, the daring usurpations of his subjects would shrink before him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "Herbert, attorney general, appeared in the house of peers and in his majesty's name entered an accusation of high treason against Lord Kimbolton and five commoners, Hollis, Sir Arthur Hazlerig, Hambden, Pym, and Strode.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "The whole world stood amazed at this important accusation, so suddenly entered upon without concert, deliberation, or reflection.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000030_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000030_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "These five members, at least Pym, Hambden and Hollis, are the very heads of the popular party; and if these be taken off, what fate must be expected by their followers, who are, many of them, accomplices in the same treason?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000030_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000030_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "The punishment of leaders is ever the last triumph over a broken and routed party; but surely was never before attempted, in opposition to a faction, during the full tide of its power and success.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000031_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000031_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "But men had not leisure to wonder at the indiscretion of this measure: their astonishment was excited by new attempts, still more precipitate and imprudent.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000031_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000031_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "A serjeant at arms, in the king's name, demanded of the house the five members: and was sent back without any positive answer. Messengers were employed to search for them, and arrest them.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000031_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000031_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "Their trunks, chambers, and studies were sealed and locked.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000032_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000032_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "He was accompanied by his ordinary retinue, to the number of above two hundred, armed as usual, some with halberts, some with walking swords.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000032_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000032_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "The king left them at the door, and he himself advanced alone through the hall, while all the members rose to receive him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000035_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000035_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "Yesterday I sent a serjeant at arms to demand some who, by my order, were accused of high treason.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000035_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000035_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "Instead of obedience, I received a message.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000035_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000035_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "I must here declare to you, that though no king that ever was in England could be more careful of your privileges than I shall be, yet in cases of treason no person has privilege.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000035_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000035_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "Well, since I see all the birds are flown, I do expect that you will send them to me as soon as they return.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000035_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000035_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "But I assure you, on the word of a king, I never did intend any force, but shall proceed against them in a fair and legal way; for I never meant any other.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000036_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000036_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "When the king was looking around for the accused members, he asked the speaker, who stood below, whether any of these persons were in the house.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000036_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000036_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "The speaker, falling on his knee, prudently replied, \"I have, sir, neither eyes to see nor tongue to speak in this place, but as the house is pleased to direct me, whose servant I am.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274369_000041_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274369/8226_274369_000041_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "That evening the accused members, to show the greater apprehension, removed into the city, which was their fortress.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000000_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000000_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "You speak of jealousies and fears.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000000_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000000_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "Lay your hands on your hearts, and ask yourselves whether I may not likewise be disturbed with fears and jealousies, and if so, I assure you that this message has nothing lessened them.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "\"As to the militia, I thought so much of it before I gave that answer, and am so much assured that the answer is agreeable to what in justice or reason you can ask, or I in honor grant, that I shall not alter it in any point.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "\"What would you have?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000003_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000003_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "I do not ask what you have done for me.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000004_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000004_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "All this considered, there is a judgment of Heaven upon this nation if these distractions continue.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "The small interval of time which had passed since the fatal accusation of the members, had been sufficient to open the eyes of many, and to recover them from the astonishment with which at first they had been seized.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000017_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000017_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "So obvious indeed was the king's present inability to invade the constitution, that the fears and jealousies which operated on the people, and pushed them so furiously to arms, were undoubtedly not of a civil, but of a religious nature.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "Each party was now willing to throw on its antagonist the odium of commencing a civil war; but both of them prepared for an event which they deemed inevitable.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000020_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000020_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "To determine his choice in the approaching contests, every man hearkened with avidity to the reasons proposed on both sides.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000020_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000020_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "The war of the pen preceded that of the sword, and daily sharpened the humors of the opposite parties.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000020_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000020_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "Besides private adventurers without number, the king and parliament themselves carried on the controversy by messages, remonstrances, and declarations; where the nation was really the party to whom all arguments were addressed.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000020_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000020_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "Charles had here a double advantage.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000020_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000020_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "Lord Falkland had accepted the office of secretary; a man who adorned the purest virtue, with the richest gifts of nature, and the most valuable acquisitions of learning.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000020_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000020_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "By him, assisted by the king himself, were the memorials of the royal party chiefly composed.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "Though these writings were of consequence, and tended much to reconcile the nation to Charles, it was evident that they would not be decisive, and that keener weapons must determine the controversy.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000024_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000024_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "To the ordinance of the parliament concerning the militia, the king opposed his commissions of array.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000024_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000024_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "The counties obeyed the one or the other, according as they stood affected.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "The magazine of Hull contained the arms of all the forces levied against the Scots; and Sir john Hotham, the governor, though he had accepted of a commission from the parliament, was not thought to be much disaffected to the church and monarchy.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "Charles therefore entertained hopes that if he presented himself at Hull before the commencement of hostilities, Hotham, overawed by his presence, would admit him with his retinue; after which he might easily render himself master of the place.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000025_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000025_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "He shut the gates, and refused to receive the king, who desired leave to enter with twenty persons only.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000032_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000032_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "Within ten days, vast quantities of plate were brought to their treasurers.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000032_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000032_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "Hardly were there men enough to receive it, or room sufficient to stow it; and many with regret were obliged to carry back their offerings, and wait till the treasurers could find leisure to receive them; such zeal animated the pious partisans of the parliament, especially in the city.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000036_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000036_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "Meanwhile the splendor of the nobility with which the king was environed much eclipsed the appearance at Westminster.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000036_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000036_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "Lord Keeper Littleton, after sending the great seal before him, had fled to York.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000036_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000036_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "Near the moiety, too, of the lower house absented themselves from counsels which they deemed so full of danger.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000036_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000036_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "The commons sent up an impeachment against nine peers, for deserting their duty in parliament.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000036_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000036_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "Their own members, also, who should return to them, they voted not to admit till satisfied concerning the reason of their absence.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000040_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000040_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "The queen, disposing of the crown jewels in Holland, had been enabled to purchase a cargo of arms and ammunition.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000040_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000040_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "Part of these, after escaping many perils, arrived safely to the king.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000040_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000040_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "His preparations were not near so forward as those of the parliament.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000040_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000040_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "In order to remove all jealousy, he had resolved that their usurpations and illegal pretensions should be apparent to the whole world; and thought that to recover the confidence of the people was a point much more material to his interest, than the collecting of any magazines, stores, or armies which might breed apprehensions of violent or illegal counsels.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000040_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000040_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "He now prepared himself for defence.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8226_274371_000040_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8226/274371/8226_274371_000040_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8226",
        "content": "From the mixed character, indeed, of Charles, arose in part the misfortunes in which England was at this time involved.",
